
	To achieve data driven framwork
	
	1. Create external files - (excel sheets, notepad files, properties files, database, spreadsheets, etc...)
	2. Connection of the external files with written code like (read the data from files & write the data in files)
	3. New library for connection with files APACHE POI
	4. We can read the data, write the data into the files
	5. Also we can integrate Data driven framework with TestNG
	
	Resources-
	- create external test data files
	- download apache poi library- https://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.lua/poi/release/bin/poi-bin-5.0.0-20210120.zip
	- unzip the downloaded folder and then import in the project 
	